headline: Pinnacle West Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: PHOENIX, June 18, 2025--Pinnacle West Capital Corp.’s board of directors today declared a quarterly dividend of $0.895 per share of common stock, payable on Sept. 2, 2025.
